dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 10 meter contour intervals and hachures. Map does not have a legend. In note: SĒM: Hē schediasia tou paronos fyllou egeneto ex anagōgēs chartōn 1:10.000 tou lekanopediou Athēnōn eis to Hypourgeion Anoikodomēseōs apo tou Noembriou 1947 mechri Maiou 1948 kai exetypōthē eis prōtēn dichrōmon ekdosin kata mēna Iounion 1948. Pasa anatypōsis tou chartou aneu adeias tou Ypourgeiou apagoreuetai. ΣΕΜ: Η σχεδίασια τοῦ παρόνος φύλλου εγένετο εξ αναγωγῆς χαρτῶν 1:10.000 τοῦ λεκανοπεδίου Αθηνῶν εις τό Υπουργεῖον Ανοικοδομήσεως από τοῦ Νοεμβρίου 1947 μέχρι Μαίου 1948 καί εξετυπώθη εις πρώτην δίχρωμον έκδοσιν κατά μῆνα Ιούνιον 1948. Πᾶσα ανατύπωσις τοῦ χάρτου άνευ αδείας τοῦ Υπουργείου απαγορεύεται. The design of this sheet was made from a reduction of 1:10,000 maps of the Athens Basin by the Ministry of Reconstruction from November 1947 to May 1948 and was printed in a first two-color edition in June 1948. Any reprinting of the map without the permission of the Ministry is prohibited. Relief shown by contours. Hypourgeion Oikismou kai Anoikodomeseos. In note: SĒM ... 1947, 1948. Greece. Hypourgeion Demosion Ergon. Hypourgeion oikismou k. anoikodomeseos. Map does not have a legend. Relief shown by 10 m. contour intervals.
